review_text:
I used the state boat ramp at Red Bridge. It was recently reconstructed. Very nice.
The boat ramp and the parking lot was redone.
A much needed improvement. Nice job done.
Only one criticism. The sanican was very dirty and needed cleaning badly. People can be so disgusting!
Love this river! Its so relaxing
Please clean up after yourselves, we all want to fish in a clean spot
BEST PLACE IN THE WORLD GONNA GO BACK SOMEDAY. :)
